channel.title: LYNXSCAPE V5.0 [I'm Back, Its been a Year]
channel.description:
I Made this Server using the base of PimpScape
NOT LEECHED
HOWEVER, IF YOU SAY THAT I HAVE LEECHED ANY OF THIS, THEN IT WILL BE REMOVED!!
OLD VERSION (History)
* Added New Home * Added New Training * Added New Shops * Added New PKing * Added Anti-Crash * Added Anti-Null * Added Anti-SYIPKPKER * Added Anti-Dupe * Added New Models * Added Pest Control (with timers) * Added New Items * Added New Commands (instead of ::pickup its now ::item) * Added Random Events * Added D Claws, D Plate, D Pickaxe, DFull Helm, Barrows * Added Switching Mage Books
NEW VERSION
* Added New Home * Added Tele Tab (Emote Tab) * Removed Horrid Panel at Top * Added New Training
